	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Fx3 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">- I added a poll to this topic.</div>
<br />I care about accuracy <strong>a lot</strong> when developing NES programs. When playing I just expect the games to work like they do on hardware, but since that's usually a side effect of accuracy, well...

		

		</td>
